<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٣٩٩٦ - حَدَّثَنِي <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1822">خَلِيفَةُ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5771">مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ عَبْدِ اللهِ الْأَنْصَارِيُّ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2332">سَعِيدٌ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5183">قَتَادَةَ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/822">أَنَسٍ </a><span class="special">﵁</span> قَالَ: <span class="c2">«مَاتَ أَبُو زَيْدٍ، وَلَمْ يَتْرُكْ عَقِبًا، وَكَانَ بَدْرِيًّا»</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>